state["opal relay"] = { seq: 2, active: true }
event = { seq: 1, retry: true }
apply(state, event)  // 현재 active가 false가 됨

This request arose during an ownership change just before handoff; the focus is the case where only the fallback channel works. The field notes were written at different times, and the new operator does not know the full history. The actual task is still bounded: for the case where only the fallback channel works in Solidity time lock, trace the reproduction and locate the defect. Avoid extra assumptions and provide only the reproduced cause and a minimal fix.

